                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="soJcCy" outputclass=" Ctr" class="- topic/p ">$3,000</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="xqiJev" class="- topic/p ">Supplies or services- If purchases are made from CONUS vendors for use overseas, the micro-purchase threshold of $3,000 remains in effect.</p>
