                  <entry morerows="2" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="WYtacR" outputclass=" Ctr" class="- topic/p ">FAR 13.201 paragraph (g)(1)(i) &amp; (ii)FAR Part 18.2FAR 2.101FAC 2005-45FAR Case 2008-024DFARS 213.301</p>
                  </entry>
