                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Checks</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="CAVOsO" outputclass=" Ctr" class="- topic/p ">$3,000</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry morerows="2" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="sHfeTv" class="- topic/p ">With the exception of contingency or emergency operations, convenience checks shall not be written over:</p>
                     <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li id="DTIYUp" class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="j3v47yki" class="- topic/p ">$3,000 for supplies,</p>
                        </li>
                        <li id="NXUFjW" class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="znj528xp" class="- topic/p ">$2,500 for services covered by the Service Contract Labor Standards statute, and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li id="hiTBAs" class="- topic/li ">
                           <p id="kcb7nm7wm" class="- topic/p ">$2,000 for construction covered by the Construction Wage Rate Requirements Statute.</p>
                        </li>
