                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Peacekeeping</b>
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Operations</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="nIUCBO" outputclass=" Ctr" class="- topic/p ">May be adjusted IAW applicable act or order</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="uzFkYr" class="- topic/p ">As authorized by a specific appropriation or an Executive Order, the micro-purchase threshold may be adjusted in accordance with the applicable act or the order.</p>
                  </entry>
