                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="lzKBFR" class="- topic/p ">
                        <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Military Tuition Assistance (MTA)</u> - Single purchase limits for MTA is set commensurate to the level of the consolidated GPC invoice submitted by each university or college.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="FEZhcJ" outputclass=" Ctr" class="- topic/p ">AFARS 5113.270-90 paragraph (g)</p>
