                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="pLYvEO" outputclass=" Ctr" class="- topic/p ">Thresholds do not apply</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p id="funrSV" class="- topic/p ">Self-service copiers are used only when necessary to satisfy needs that are impractical for sending to DLA Document Services due to size or time constraints. The GPC is not used to purchase printing and reproduction services directly from a commercial vendor unless a waiver has been obtained through DLA Document Services. The Lighthouse for the Blind, Inc., and UNICOR, may be used (without a waiver) as an alternate source of procuring services when it is clearly less costly to the Army.</p>
